The '''''Firrinree''''' was one of the two [[Sh'ner-class planetary assault carrier]]s in the [[Keeramak Entourage]] during the [[Battle of Bakura (28 ABY)|battle of Bakura]] in [[28 ABY/Legends|28 ABY]]. The ship eventually fell into the hands of the [[P'w'eck]]s during the battle when they overthrew their [[Ssi-ruu]]k overlords.

